content:
Rada's blessings are rewards from the Kourend & Kebos Diary obtained by speaking to Elise in the Kourend Castle courtyard. The different upgrades of Rada's blessings are:

  • Rada's blessing 1, from the easy tasks set
  • Rada's blessing 2, from the medium tasks set
  • Rada's blessing 3, from the hard tasks set
  • Rada's blessing 4, from the elite tasks set

rawContent:
'''Rada's blessings''' are rewards from the [[Kourend & Kebos Diary]] obtained by speaking to [[Elise]] in the [[Kourend Castle]] courtyard. The different upgrades of Rada's blessings are:

*[[Rada's blessing 1]], from the easy tasks set
*[[Rada's blessing 2]], from the medium tasks set
*[[Rada's blessing 3]], from the hard tasks set
*[[Rada's blessing 4]], from the elite tasks set
